</p>
<p>Make this extend the same <code>BaseController</code> from our project and let's get to work!</p>
<p>First create a <code>public function newTokenAction()</code>. Add the <code>@Route</code> above and let it
autocomplete so that the <code>use</code> statement is added for the annotation. Set the URL
to <code>/api/tokens</code>. Heck, let's get crazy and also add <code>@Method</code>: we only want this
route to match for POST requests:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="5a89451779">
    <div class="meta">
