<h2 id="checking-the-username-and-password">Checking the Username and Password <a class="headerlink" href="create-json-web-token#checking-the-username-and-password" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Head back to <code>TokenController</code>. Here's the process:</p>
<ol>
<li>Check that the username and password are correct.</li>
<li>Generate a JSON web token.</li>
<li>Send it back to the client.</li>
<li>High-five everyone at your office. I can't wait to get to that step.</li>
</ol>
