<div class="admonition tip"><p class="admonition-title"><span class="fa fa-lightbulb-o"></span> Tip</p><p>Don't forget to pass an <code>exp</code> key to the token, otherwise the token will <em>never</em>
expire! We forgot to do this in the video!</p>
</div><p>But you can store anything here, like roles, user information, some poetry - whatever!</p>
<p>And that's it! This is a string, so return a new <code>JsonResponse</code> with a token field
set to <code>$token</code>:</p>
