</div>
</p>
<p>Check for a 401 status code. Copy the method name and go run that test:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/phpunit --filter testPOSTTokenInvalidCredentials</div></code></pre>
<p>It should pass... but it doesn't! Interesting. Look at this: it definitely doesn't
return the token... it redirected us to <code>/login</code>. We <em>are</em> getting kicked out of
the controller, but this is <em>not</em> how we want our API error responses to work.
We'll fix this a bit later.</p>

    
